snippet: Keeneland's September Yearling Sale topped the $100 million mark with celebrity chef Bobby Flay breeding one of two fillies that were purchased for at least $1.1 million each....

headline.print_headline: Keeneland Yearling Sales Top $100 Million Mark
headline.main: Keeneland Yearling Sales Top $100 Million Mark

lead_paragraph: Keeneland's September Yearling Sale topped the $100 million mark with celebrity chef Bobby Flay breeding one of two fillies that were purchased for at least $1.1 million each.
